name: WinBackup Archive
summary: Learn about .WBB files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: WinBackup can back up data to a variety of different media, including hard drives, network drives, removable drives, and portable USB drives. It can also save data to optical media, such as CD-R/RW and DVD-R/RW discs.
WinBackup 2, the final version of WinBackup, was discontinued by Uniblue in 2007.
